OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early cloud will likely
OL,6,Ffade away, to leave a largely sunny
OL,7,Fmorning. Turning very warm with only
OL,8,Flight winds. Sunshine likely turning
OL,9,Fhazy through the afternoon, as some
OL,10,Fhigher cloud spreads south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud is likely to thicken
OL,13,Ffrom the west overnight, however
OL,14,Foccasional clear spells will also
OL,15,Fallow for some mist or fog patches to
OL,16,Fdevelop by dawn. Mild with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
