OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FBrighter spells likely
OL,6,Fthrough the morning, with the best of
OL,7,Fany warm sunshine east. Cloud then
OL,8,Fthickens further by the afternoon,
OL,9,Fwith outbreaks of rain later. Cooler
OL,10,Fthan on Wednesday.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FChilly
OL,13,Fstart Friday then sunny intervals.
OL,14,FVariable cloud Saturday, perhaps some
OL,15,Fshowers, but also brighter intervals.
OL,16,FSunshine and showers Sunday.
OL,17,FTemperatures near normal for April.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
